title: 13 Lissa Rankin: How to Heal Yourself with the Power of Your Mind
description: Did you know you could heal yourself from the worst cases of illness and physical pain without medicine or the use of a doctor? Sounds crazy, right? I've experienced this first hand and seen how powerful your mind can be in healing yourself (even in some extreme cases of broken bones, and energy sucking sickness). […]
